  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT271-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ vāyil nērntu pukka tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered by HER to the confidante when HE entered after
          having been granted the door/mediation. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT271">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> aruvi yaṉṉa paruvuṟai citaṟi</l>
          <l> yāṟuniṟai pakaru nāṭaṉait tēṟi</l>
          <l> yuṟṟatu maṉṉu morunāṇ maṟṟatu</l>
          <l> tavappaṉ ṉāṭōṇ mayaṅki</l>
          <l> vauvum paṇpi ṉōyā kiṉṟē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Believing the man from the land where the river voices [its] fullness</l>
          <l rend="indent2">[and] scatters big drops like a waterfall,</l>
          <l>it happened, in fact. </l>
          <l rend="indent7">One day only [was] that.</l>
          <l>Very many days [my] shoulders have been confused</l>
          <l><choice>
              <seg>[and that] of a nature which attracts became pain.</seg>
              <seg>[and] it became pain of the gripping kind.</seg>
            </choice></l>

          <lg type="alternate">
            <l> Believing the man from the land where the river voices [its] fullness</l>
            <l rend="indent2"> [and] scatters big drops like a waterfall,</l>
            <l> it happened, in fact, one day.</l>
            <l rend="indent7"> But that [same thing],</l>
            <l rend="indent2"> after distressing [my] shoulders for many days,</l>
            <l> became a pain of a nature that devours.</l>
          </lg>

        </lg>
      </div>
